-- Italy's Anima sees net inflows of 284 mln euros in August 
-- 
-- Wed Sep 10, 2014 09:27AM EDT
-- None



MILAN, Sept 10 (Reuters) - Italian asset manager Anima <ANIM.MI> said on Wednesday its net inflows were 284 million euros ($366 million) in August, bringing overall inflows in the first eight months of the year to around 6.1 billion euros.

